items.description:
Array of arrays with the or conditions. Each or condiciton is an array of ands. The items in the ands arrays are key value arrays with key as field and value as condition. Javascript Example: let filter = {
    filters: [
        [
            {
                property: 'id',
                value: 1,
                condition: '='
            }
        ],
        [
            {
                property: 'id',
                value: 5,
                condition: '>='
            },
            {
                property: 'id',
                value: 7,
                condition: '<='
            }
        ]
    ]
}; This means id = 1 || (id >= 5 && id <= 7) || id = 1
